Package: HeterogeneityASE
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Shrinkage Estimator for Meta-Analysis Heterogeneity
Version: 0.3.0
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Authors@R: person("Mahmood Ul", "Hassan",
    email = "CORRESPONDING_EMAIL_PLACEHOLDER",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "ORCID_PLACEHOLDER"))
Description: Implements a conflict-aware Empirical Bayes shrinkage estimator
    for inter-study heterogeneity (tau-squared) in meta-analysis. Uses
    outcome-specific priors derived from 17,236 Cochrane meta-analyses
    (Pairwise70 dataset) to stabilize estimation in small-sample scenarios.
    Supports the Hartung-Knapp-Sidik-Jonkman adjustment for pooled effects.
